When Termitron catches up with her, she continues, "Remember how we 
got here? You were flying?" She reminds Termitron. "Well, that's how 
we're going to have to get out of here again." She smiles then 
frowns, thinking that flying isn't her favorite thing to do, even 
when necessary.
